# AXION MONTESSORI — MASTER CURSOR PROMPT

Do NOT alter architecture, design tokens, or role logic. Fix only broken code.

## Project identity

- **App:** Axion — Montessori Management System
- **Stack:** React Native (Expo) · Node.js + Express · MongoDB via Prisma · Socket.io · Anthropic Claude API
- **Backend port:** `http://127.0.0.1:8011`
- **MongoDB:** `mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/axion_montessori`

## Design tokens (DO NOT CHANGE)

Use exact values in `mobile/lib/theme.ts` (`Colors`, `Fonts`, `Radius`, `Shadow`). CSS source: `Axion.css`.

## RBAC (DO NOT CHANGE)

| Feature | ADMIN | TEACHER | PARENT |
|---|---|---|---|
| Dashboard | School-wide stats + all classrooms | Own class stats only | Child summary + fees + AI summary |
| Students | All students, all classrooms | Own classroom only | Own child only |
| Attendance | Mark + edit + reports for all | Mark own classroom, leave option | View child's record only |
| CCTV | All cameras | Own classroom + playground | Child's classroom only (view-only) |
| Messages | Broadcast to all roles | Class broadcast + parent DM | DM teacher/admin only |
| Fees | Manage all fees, set overdue | No access | View own child's fees + history |
| Notices | Send to any/all groups | Send to parents of own class | Receive only |
| Complaints | View + resolve all | File + view own | File + view own |
| AI Chatbot | Full analytics query | Class-level query | Child-level query only |
| Leaderboard | Full board | Own class board | Child's rank + class board |
| Schools | Register + manage all | No access | No access |

## Implementation order (1–14)

1. Prisma schema → `prisma db push` → comprehensive `prisma/seed.js`
2. Auth routes (login/register/me) + JWT middleware
3. Encryption utility on message routes
4. Socket.io server with room-based auth
5. REST routes: students → classrooms → attendance → observations → messages → fees → complaints → notices → notifications → schools
6. AI service (`src/services/ai.js`)
7. Fee + weekly summary cron (`src/jobs/feeChecker.js`)
8. Expo Router scaffold
9. Auth flow (SecureStore, role-aware nav)
10. Screens: Dashboard → Students → Attendance → Messages → Fees → My Child → AI Chat → Detection → Leaderboard → Notices → Complaints → Schools
11. Socket.io client (messages + notifications)
12. Expo push notifications
13. Biometric auth, haptics, skeletons, empty states, offline
14. QA all three roles on iOS + Android

## Data integrity

- `prisma/seed-users.js` — **only** three demo users (do not change their emails)
- `prisma/seed.js` — 1 school, 3 classrooms, 6 students (2/class), fees, teacher per class, parent per student

